[21-06-2026 04:30:00 PM] Identified inconsistency between VMDK flat file and descriptor.
[21-06-2026 05:00:00 PM] Traced cause to storage cache failure during snapshot consolidation.
[21-06-2026 06:00:00 PM] Initiated restoration of disk files from backup storage.
[21-06-2026 08:00:00 PM] Re-registered VM with restored virtual disk.
[21-06-2026 09:30:00 PM] Verified data integrity; booted VM; resumed service.

